WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:03.669
Good morning, family. Praise the Lord. I

00:00:03.679 --> 00:00:07.269
believe this is day 10, if I'm not

00:00:07.279 --> 00:00:10.230
mistaken.

00:00:10.240 --> 00:00:11.910
We're in the double

00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:14.150
digits. Maybe it's day 11;

00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:17.029
I'll have to ask my son. It all goes

00:00:17.039 --> 00:00:19.830
together for me, but I had

00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:22.150
some things on my heart.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:26.710
The Lord

00:00:26.720 --> 00:00:28.870
wants me to bring it up again.

00:00:28.880 --> 00:00:32.790
Jesus is the Healer.

00:00:35.920 --> 00:00:37.430
I've been thinking about it

00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:40.069
because of the meetings I've been

00:00:40.079 --> 00:00:43.430
in the last three days. People

00:00:43.430 --> 00:00:43.440
are

00:00:43.440 --> 00:00:46.150
getting healed. I'm seeing people

00:00:46.160 --> 00:00:47.990
walk away

00:00:47.990 --> 00:00:48.000
believing

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:49.510
for their manifestation,

00:00:49.510 --> 00:00:49.520
while

00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:51.110
some get

00:00:51.110 --> 00:00:51.120
theirs

00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:53.590
instantaneously.

00:00:53.600 --> 00:00:57.029
You see the bondage of

00:00:57.039 --> 00:00:59.189
Satan's work falling off.

00:00:59.199 --> 00:01:02.549
I know beyond a shadow of a doubt

00:01:02.559 --> 00:01:06.630
we are about to see great

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:09.670
manifestations of the glory of God

00:01:09.680 --> 00:01:12.950
beyond anybody's comprehension. We are

00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:15.750
in the last seconds of the last days.

00:01:15.760 --> 00:01:16.870
I'm going to

00:01:16.880 --> 00:01:20.310
keep saying it: Jesus Christ is coming.

00:01:20.320 --> 00:01:22.710
There's a work to be

00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:25.109
done; the harvest is

00:01:25.119 --> 00:01:27.670
plentiful, but the laborers are few.

00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:30.550
I pray you are being a

00:01:30.560 --> 00:01:32.710
light in the

00:01:32.710 --> 00:01:32.720
darkness—at

00:01:32.720 --> 00:01:35.350
your workplace, the

00:01:35.360 --> 00:01:37.510
store,

00:01:37.510 --> 00:01:37.520
or

00:01:37.520 --> 00:01:39.670
school.

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:44.149
Be a light shining bright

00:01:44.159 --> 00:01:47.109
for the world to see.

00:01:49.119 --> 00:01:51.990
There was

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:55.670
a night I was praying and one of

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:57.910
my friends called. They were

00:01:57.920 --> 00:02:01.350
overcoming severe arthritis.

00:02:04.719 --> 00:02:07.429
He asked me, 'Brandon, why

00:02:07.429 --> 00:02:07.439
aren't

00:02:07.439 --> 00:02:09.190
all

00:02:09.200 --> 00:02:11.029
Christians

00:02:11.029 --> 00:02:11.039
healed?'I

00:02:11.039 --> 00:02:14.550
told

00:02:14.550 --> 00:02:14.560
him

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:17.270
I

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:19.589
don't have all the answers, but I'll

00:02:19.599 --> 00:02:22.070
ask the Lord.

00:02:27.280 --> 00:02:28.790
It bothered me because

00:02:30.640 --> 00:02:32.309
some people I pray

00:02:32.309 --> 00:02:32.319
for

00:02:32.319 --> 00:02:33.509
get healed and some

00:02:33.519 --> 00:02:35.589
don't.

00:02:36.949 --> 00:02:36.959
You

00:02:38.869 --> 00:02:38.879
can

00:02:42.080 --> 00:02:44.630
get weary

00:02:47.200 --> 00:02:49.350
in

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:54.470
well-doing.

00:02:56.959 --> 00:03:00.390
I heard a message from

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:04.470
a preacher who said to always stay on God's

00:03:04.480 --> 00:03:06.869
side, even if you don't understand

00:03:06.879 --> 00:03:08.470
what you're walking through.

00:03:08.480 --> 00:03:11.670
Never

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:15.589
get angry at God. Like Job,

00:03:15.589 --> 00:03:15.599
who

00:03:15.599 --> 00:03:19.030
stood his ground:

00:03:19.040 --> 00:03:20.869
'Though He slay me, yet will I praise Him.'No

00:03:20.869 --> 00:03:20.879
matter

00:03:20.879 --> 00:03:24.550
the

00:03:24.550 --> 00:03:24.560
circumstance,

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:27.190
God

00:03:27.200 --> 00:03:29.589
is a

00:03:29.599 --> 00:03:32.309
good God.

00:03:53.360 --> 00:03:55.910
People

00:03:55.920 --> 00:03:58.070
in the body of Christ,

00:03:58.080 --> 00:03:59.750
even in the Word of Faith

00:03:59.760 --> 00:04:02.390
movement,

00:04:02.390 --> 00:04:02.400
often

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:04.070
don't answer the hard questions.

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:05.990
Brother Hagin always

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:08.630
did. That's why I go through

00:04:08.640 --> 00:04:11.110
the old archives from Brother Hagin

00:04:11.110 --> 00:04:11.120
and

00:04:11.120 --> 00:04:14.869
feast as much as I can.

00:04:21.759 --> 00:04:24.390
He was a diamond in the rough of all the

00:04:24.400 --> 00:04:25.909
ministers I've listened to.

00:04:25.919 --> 00:04:28.310
Brother Hagin changed my life;

00:04:28.320 --> 00:04:30.230
he had a

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:33.590
teaching anointing.

00:04:33.600 --> 00:04:35.590
I wish he

00:04:35.590 --> 00:04:35.600
were

00:04:35.600 --> 00:04:38.950
still here, but his season

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:40.710
was over.

00:04:47.680 --> 00:04:51.990
I went to sleep that night and had

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:53.830
an experience with the Lord.

00:05:30.960 --> 00:05:34.629
In this experience,

00:05:34.639 --> 00:05:38.550
I was

00:05:38.560 --> 00:05:43.670
at

00:05:43.670 --> 00:05:43.680
Jesus'crucifixion.

00:05:43.680 --> 00:05:46.710
He was a young man,

00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:58.550
33 years old.

00:06:01.990 --> 00:06:02.000
I

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:06.469
saw

00:06:09.680 --> 00:06:13.270
him right before

00:06:13.270 --> 00:06:13.280
he

00:06:13.280 --> 00:06:15.909
was

00:06:15.919 --> 00:06:19.189
scourged.

00:06:19.199 --> 00:06:21.990
I

00:06:24.790 --> 00:06:24.800
was

00:06:26.639 --> 00:06:30.070
standing there with the Father

00:06:30.070 --> 00:06:30.080
and

00:06:30.080 --> 00:06:35.350
Jesus, watching Jesus in the past

00:06:35.350 --> 00:06:35.360
being

00:06:35.360 --> 00:06:38.469
whipped.

00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:52.790
It felt like real time. I could smell the

00:06:52.790 --> 00:06:52.800
livestock and

00:06:52.800 --> 00:06:55.189
the animal

00:06:55.189 --> 00:06:55.199
feces. The

00:06:55.199 --> 00:06:58.710
sun was

00:06:58.710 --> 00:06:58.720
shining and

00:06:58.720 --> 00:07:01.589
it felt

00:07:33.199 --> 00:07:35.589
about

00:07:41.599 --> 00:07:44.870
85 degrees.

00:07:44.880 --> 00:07:47.430
His skin was sweating and

00:07:47.430 --> 00:07:47.440
dirty;

00:07:47.440 --> 00:07:50.070
he was

00:07:50.070 --> 00:07:50.080
olive-complected.

00:07:50.080 --> 00:07:53.430
His

00:07:53.440 --> 00:07:57.270
hands

00:07:57.280 --> 00:08:00.710
were

00:08:05.029 --> 00:08:05.039
strapped

00:08:06.950 --> 00:08:06.960
by

00:08:14.319 --> 00:08:16.869
metal bands to

00:08:16.869 --> 00:08:16.879
a

00:08:16.879 --> 00:08:19.110
whipping post. There

00:08:19.110 --> 00:08:19.120
were

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:22.790
two soldiers. One

00:08:32.320 --> 00:08:36.310
was a very large man,

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:38.070
bald,

00:08:38.080 --> 00:08:40.790
and

00:08:40.800 --> 00:08:45.190
massively

00:08:48.630 --> 00:08:48.640
built.

00:08:52.150 --> 00:08:52.160
The

00:08:54.070 --> 00:08:54.080
other

00:08:56.800 --> 00:08:59.590
was a Roman guard with a breastplate

00:08:59.590 --> 00:08:59.600
and a kilt-looking

00:08:59.600 --> 00:09:01.750
outfit.

00:09:12.720 --> 00:09:15.030
They

00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:27.030
were cracking those whips to

00:09:27.030 --> 00:09:27.040
intimidate him.

00:09:27.040 --> 00:09:29.030
I saw

00:09:29.030 --> 00:09:29.040
them

00:09:29.040 --> 00:09:32.070
whip

00:09:58.720 --> 00:10:02.949
him,

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:08.710
and blood

00:10:08.720 --> 00:10:11.030
splattered everywhere. Chunks

00:10:11.030 --> 00:10:11.040
of flesh

00:10:11.040 --> 00:10:13.509
were pulled

00:10:13.509 --> 00:10:13.519
from

00:10:13.519 --> 00:10:17.190
his body.

00:10:39.440 --> 00:10:42.310
I screamed,

00:10:42.320 --> 00:10:45.190
'Stop

00:10:47.350 --> 00:10:47.360
it!'I

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:53.269
saw

00:10:53.279 --> 00:10:55.910
them ripping his beard out.

00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:58.069
They tortured him

00:11:09.360 --> 00:11:12.150
as they tore him to pieces.

00:11:17.200 --> 00:11:19.590
When they were done, he

00:11:19.600 --> 00:11:22.550
dangled there as a bloody mess. His

00:11:33.120 --> 00:11:35.430
rib

00:11:47.269 --> 00:11:47.279
bones

00:11:58.800 --> 00:12:00.230
were

00:12:03.200 --> 00:12:05.829
showing

00:12:05.839 --> 00:12:08.150
because they whipped

00:12:08.160 --> 00:12:10.389
him so much.

00:12:10.399 --> 00:12:12.790
The Lord spoke to me

00:12:12.790 --> 00:12:12.800
and

00:12:12.800 --> 00:12:15.750
said,

00:12:18.560 --> 00:12:23.829
'Brandon, by my stripes

00:12:23.839 --> 00:12:29.110
you are healed. The

00:12:29.120 --> 00:12:32.949
same faith it took to ask for

00:12:32.959 --> 00:12:36.550
forgiveness of sins is the same

00:12:36.550 --> 00:12:36.560
faith

00:12:36.560 --> 00:12:39.430
for

00:12:39.430 --> 00:12:39.440
healing.'He

00:12:39.440 --> 00:12:43.030
said

00:12:46.069 --> 00:12:46.079
you

00:12:49.200 --> 00:12:52.389
would never question your

00:12:52.399 --> 00:12:54.629
salvation;

00:13:51.440 --> 00:13:53.509
you're fully persuaded.

00:14:03.600 --> 00:14:06.150
But people question

00:14:06.150 --> 00:14:06.160
the

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:09.189
stripes more

00:14:09.199 --> 00:14:11.990
than the sin issue.

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:13.509
He said, 'I took

00:14:13.509 --> 00:14:13.519
your sickness, disease,

00:14:13.519 --> 00:14:15.829
sin, and poverty.'Faith

00:14:15.829 --> 00:14:15.839
and healing are

00:14:15.839 --> 00:14:18.389
not feelings, just as salvation isn't. If I

00:14:18.389 --> 00:14:18.399
confess my sins, He is faithful to

00:14:18.399 --> 00:14:21.430
forgive. Likewise, by His stripes, you are healed.

00:14:21.430 --> 00:14:21.440
His words are life and health to

00:14:21.440 --> 00:14:23.590
all their

00:14:23.590 --> 00:14:23.600
flesh.

00:14:23.600 --> 00:14:25.829
The

00:14:25.829 --> 00:14:25.839
Lord

00:14:25.839 --> 00:14:28.310
told me,

00:14:28.310 --> 00:14:28.320
'When

00:14:28.320 --> 00:14:31.750
you

00:14:31.750 --> 00:14:31.760
believe

00:14:31.760 --> 00:14:35.590
for your

00:14:35.600 --> 00:14:37.430
healing

00:14:37.430 --> 00:14:37.440
as

00:14:41.269 --> 00:14:41.279
much

00:14:41.279 --> 00:14:44.150
as

00:14:44.160 --> 00:14:46.710
your

00:14:46.720 --> 00:14:48.629
salvation,

00:14:48.639 --> 00:14:51.910
the manifestation

00:14:54.389 --> 00:14:54.399
comes.'Don't

00:15:00.470 --> 00:15:00.480
doubt

00:15:02.160 --> 00:15:03.990
in

00:15:05.920 --> 00:15:08.629
your

00:15:11.030 --> 00:15:11.040
heart.

00:15:15.030 --> 00:15:15.040
Life

00:15:16.880 --> 00:15:18.949
and

00:15:22.480 --> 00:15:24.710
death

00:15:28.870 --> 00:15:28.880
are

00:15:32.870 --> 00:15:32.880
in

00:15:34.480 --> 00:15:37.829
the

00:15:41.120 --> 00:15:43.990
power

00:15:47.110 --> 00:15:47.120
of

00:15:53.990 --> 00:15:54.000
the

00:15:56.560 --> 00:15:58.629
tongue.

00:16:01.759 --> 00:16:04.470
I'm not moved by a symptom;

00:16:04.470 --> 00:16:04.480
I am

00:16:04.480 --> 00:16:06.870
moved by

00:16:06.880 --> 00:16:08.710
the Word.

00:19:58.080 --> 00:20:00.390
You don't have to earn your healing; it's a finished

00:20:00.400 --> 00:20:03.909
work.

00:20:07.600 --> 00:20:09.430
It's by

00:20:09.440 --> 00:20:11.990
grace you are saved through faith.

00:20:58.720 --> 00:21:01.830
Not one of us should be suffering with

00:21:01.840 --> 00:21:03.510
sickness.

00:21:08.159 --> 00:21:12.310
Freely He gave,

00:21:12.320 --> 00:21:14.870
and freely we receive.

00:21:36.320 --> 00:21:38.950
He made us

00:21:38.950 --> 00:21:38.960
joint-heirs,

00:21:38.960 --> 00:21:40.950
seated with Him in the heavenlies.

00:21:40.950 --> 00:21:40.960
I

00:21:40.960 --> 00:21:42.870
love

00:21:42.870 --> 00:21:42.880
the

00:21:42.880 --> 00:21:46.070
book

00:21:46.070 --> 00:21:46.080
of

00:21:46.080 --> 00:21:47.830
Ephesians.

00:21:55.440 --> 00:21:57.909
My

00:21:57.919 --> 00:21:59.669
favorite passage that Brother

00:21:59.669 --> 00:21:59.679
Hagin

00:21:59.679 --> 00:22:02.310
always talks about is when

00:22:02.320 --> 00:22:04.390
Jesus turned to the woman with the issue of

00:22:04.400 --> 00:22:06.950
blood.

00:22:09.760 --> 00:22:11.830
Her

00:22:11.840 --> 00:22:15.270
faith made

00:22:15.270 --> 00:22:15.280
her

00:22:15.280 --> 00:22:19.270
whole.

00:23:36.320 --> 00:23:40.950
If her faith can make her whole,

00:23:40.960 --> 00:23:43.750
your faith

00:23:43.760 --> 00:23:47.029
can make you whole.

00:26:27.120 --> 00:26:30.390
Today is your day for healing.

00:26:30.400 --> 00:26:32.630
I

00:26:32.640 --> 00:26:34.950
believe

00:27:59.120 --> 00:28:02.710
for

00:29:37.840 --> 00:29:40.630
your deliverance today.

00:29:44.080 --> 00:29:47.350
Believe for now; faith is

00:29:47.350 --> 00:29:47.360
the

00:29:47.360 --> 00:29:48.789
substance of things hoped for.

00:31:13.200 --> 00:31:16.549
Father, I thank You

00:31:42.399 --> 00:31:47.190
that by Your stripes they are healed.

00:32:15.600 --> 00:32:18.230
We thank You

00:34:02.080 --> 00:34:05.029
for creative miracles.

00:34:05.039 --> 00:34:07.990
I

00:34:08.000 --> 00:34:10.950
believe for

00:34:12.560 --> 00:34:15.190
glaucoma

00:34:21.599 --> 00:34:25.589
to

00:34:28.320 --> 00:34:30.069
be healed

00:34:30.069 --> 00:34:30.079
and coronary

00:34:30.079 --> 00:34:33.030
arteries to

00:34:33.030 --> 00:34:33.040
be

00:34:33.040 --> 00:34:35.030
unclogged. No

00:34:35.030 --> 00:34:35.040
Alzheimer's, no

00:34:35.040 --> 00:34:37.669
dementia. I

00:34:37.669 --> 00:34:37.679
saw

00:34:37.679 --> 00:34:41.270
silos

00:34:41.280 --> 00:34:45.270
full of body parts in heaven waiting

00:34:45.280 --> 00:34:47.349
for

00:34:47.359 --> 00:34:49.589
manifestations. I

00:34:49.599 --> 00:34:52.310
believe for arms and legs to grow back.

00:35:49.200 --> 00:35:53.030
Father,

00:35:53.040 --> 00:35:56.470
we pray over this

00:35:56.480 --> 00:36:02.950
nation

00:36:02.960 --> 00:36:04.870
and this

00:36:04.880 --> 00:36:07.750
election.

00:36:50.000 --> 00:36:54.790
We call forth a

00:36:54.800 --> 00:36:57.510
Godly nation.

00:37:03.030 --> 00:37:03.040
We

00:37:06.240 --> 00:37:08.310
call for

00:37:56.720 --> 00:38:00.630
a fair election

00:38:18.720 --> 00:38:20.950
and

00:38:40.480 --> 00:38:42.550
pray

00:38:57.119 --> 00:38:59.750
for

00:38:59.760 --> 00:39:02.470
divine protection over Donald

00:39:02.470 --> 00:39:02.480
Trump—over

00:39:02.480 --> 00:39:03.990
his

00:39:03.990 --> 00:39:04.000
food

00:39:04.000 --> 00:39:06.069
and

00:39:06.069 --> 00:39:06.079
drink.

00:39:06.079 --> 00:39:08.870
No weapon formed against him

00:39:08.870 --> 00:39:08.880
shall

00:39:08.880 --> 00:39:11.190
prosper.

00:39:11.190 --> 00:39:11.200
We

00:39:11.200 --> 00:39:13.750
stand

00:39:13.750 --> 00:39:13.760
in

00:39:13.760 --> 00:39:17.109
the

00:39:17.119 --> 00:39:19.030
gap

00:39:19.030 --> 00:39:19.040
for

00:39:19.040 --> 00:39:21.510
America

00:39:21.510 --> 00:39:21.520
and

00:39:21.520 --> 00:39:24.150
Israel.

00:39:24.160 --> 00:39:26.950
Lord,

00:40:29.910 --> 00:40:29.920
expose

00:41:30.230 --> 00:41:30.240
the

00:42:25.359 --> 00:42:30.150
darkness

00:43:27.680 --> 00:43:30.550
in

00:44:27.440 --> 00:44:29.670
leadership.

00:46:23.760 --> 00:46:26.710
Expose

00:46:30.000 --> 00:46:33.270
financial corruption

00:46:37.359 --> 00:46:39.589
in

00:46:45.349 --> 00:46:45.359
the

00:46:50.790 --> 00:46:50.800
church

00:46:58.400 --> 00:47:01.270
like

00:47:28.550 --> 00:47:28.560
Ananias

00:47:52.710 --> 00:47:52.720
and

00:48:14.480 --> 00:48:16.550
Sapphira.

00:48:38.720 --> 00:48:41.430
Raise up godly leaders

00:48:41.430 --> 00:48:41.440
who preach

00:48:41.440 --> 00:48:44.630
the

00:48:44.630 --> 00:48:44.640
hard truths

00:48:44.640 --> 00:48:47.190
and not

00:48:47.190 --> 00:48:47.200
a

00:48:47.200 --> 00:48:49.670
lukewarm gospel.

00:48:49.670 --> 00:48:49.680
Wake

